<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><style>
  :root { --accent: #fbbf24; --teal: #5eead4; --pink: #fb7185; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html, body { width: 1200px; height: 675px; overflow: hidden;
    font-family: -apple-system, "Inter", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #fff;
    background:
      radial-gradient(800px 500px at 70% 90%, rgba(251,191,36,0.20), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(700px 400px at 12% 18%, rgba(251,113,133,0.16), transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0f1e 0%, #07091a 100%);
  }
  .frame { position: absolute; inset: 0; padding: 56px 64px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .title { font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 800; }

  .center { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; gap: 24px; }
  h2 {
    font-size: 64px; line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #c2c9dc);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  h2 .glow {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--pink));
    -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  .stab {
    font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.55; color: #c2c9dc; font-weight: 600;
    max-width: 920px;
  }
  .stab em { background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 60%, rgba(251,191,36,0.4) 60%);
    font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 900; padding: 0 6px; }

  .links {
    display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .link {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    border-radius: 14px;
  }
  .link .icon { font-size: 24px; }
  .link .lhs { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .link .ttl { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; }
  .link .sub2 { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-weight: 500; }
  .link.pri {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251,191,36,0.15), rgba(251,113,133,0.06));
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .bottom {
    text-align: center; padding-top: 18px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .bottom b { color: var(--accent); }
</style></head>
<body>
<div class="frame">
  <div class="title">CTA · OPEN SOURCE</div>
  <div class="center">
    <h2>Built into a reusable <span class="glow">Claude Skill</span>.<br>The whole thing is open.</h2>
    <div class="stab">
      Drop a folder of project cards into the skill.<br>
      <em>30 minutes</em> later: panoramic page, DD table, Word reports — auto-deployed.
    </div>
    <div class="links">
      <div class="link pri">
        <div class="icon">📦</div>
        <div class="lhs">
          <div class="ttl">github.com/zhanglunet/demo-day-dossier</div>
          <div class="sub2">Skill + scripts + first-run reference dataset</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="link">
        <div class="icon">🌐</div>
        <div class="lhs">
          <div class="ttl">qiji-roadshow-2026.pages.dev</div>
          <div class="sub2">Live panoramic + DD table + story</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bottom">
    <b>"It's not AI replacing thinking — it's AI clearing the busywork before you can think."</b>
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>
